@startuml
!include ../plantuml-theme.iuml
top to bottom direction

title 隐私治理链路图

skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.1
skinparam ArrowColor #666666
skinparam rectangleBorderColor #7F8C8D
skinparam rectangleBackgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam ranksep 14
skinparam nodesep 10

rectangle "输入文本 / 用户问题" as Input #FFF3E1
rectangle "敏感识别" as Detect #FDEDEC
rectangle "脱敏处理\n生成 safeText" as Sanitize #FDEDEC
rectangle "元数据标注\nrestricted / externalModelAllowed /\nsensitivityLevel" as Tag #FDEDEC

rectangle "索引视图\nsafeText + restricted + sensitivityLevel" as IndexView #E8F4FD
rectangle "外发视图\nsafeText + externalModelAllowed +\nrestricted + sensitivityLevel" as ExternalView #E8F4FD
rectangle "日志视图\nsafeText + restricted + sensitivityLevel" as LogView #E8F4FD

rectangle "模型输出" as ModelOutput #E9F7EF
rectangle "输出复核" as Review #FDEDEC

rectangle "放行" as Pass #E9F7EF
rectangle "拦截" as Block #FADBD8
rectangle "二次脱敏" as RedactAgain #FCF3CF

Input -down-> Detect
Detect -down-> Sanitize
Sanitize -down-> Tag
Tag -right-> IndexView
Tag -down-> ExternalView
Tag -left-> LogView
ExternalView -down-> ModelOutput
ModelOutput -down-> Review
Review -down-> Pass
Review -left-> Block
Review -right-> RedactAgain

note right of Detect
识别阶段覆盖三类对象：
个人身份信息、
系统凭据、
企业受限信息。
end note

note right of Sanitize
命中后执行掩码替换、
占位替换或强制清除，
统一生成 safeText。
end note

note right of Tag
把治理结果写入分块与索引记录，
供检索、外发、历史与日志链路复用。
end note

note right of IndexView
用于内部检索与索引写入。
受限内容可在授权范围内参与内部召回。
end note

note right of ExternalView
仅在 externalModelAllowed = true 时
可进入外部 Embedding 计算、
Prompt 上下文和模型外发链路。
end note

note left of LogView
日志、历史与审计仅记录治理后内容，
不保留未脱敏原文。
end note

note right of Review
生成后再次扫描敏感模式；
高风险命中时执行拦截
或再次脱敏。
end note

legend bottom
主链对应“识别 -> 脱敏 -> 标注 -> 外发 -> 复核”，
三条支路对应“索引视图 / 外发视图 / 日志视图”。
图中四个字段必须贯穿治理链路：
safeText、restricted、externalModelAllowed、sensitivityLevel。
endlegend
@enduml
